                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/3903: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-07-26T15:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 26, 1922—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>187. Your 318 July 24, 5 p.m.</p>
                <p>It is Department’s view that you should neither aid nor actively oppose proposed
                    loan which is a British enterprise. Department does not desire to curtail any
                    legitimate independent effort which Pacific Development Corporation may consider
                    advisable in obtaining liquidation of its loan.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
